<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>南昌大学在职教师证明</title>
  <meta name="description" content="南昌大学在职教师证明 — Jinrong Liu，计算机教师">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f0e8;
      --paper: #fffef9;
      --ink: #1a1a1a;
      --ink-light: #4a4a4a;
      --ink-muted: #8a8a8a;
      --red: #c0392b;
      --red-light: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.08);
      --gold: #b8860b;
      --border: #d4c5a9;
      --shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(60, 40, 10, 0.12);
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Noto Serif SC", "Source Han Serif SC", "SimSun", "Songti SC", serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--bg);
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.03), transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 80%, rgba(184, 134, 11, 0.04), transparent 50%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .page-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 820px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .certificate {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 2px;
      padding: 60px 72px 56px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .certificate::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      left: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      bottom: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 1px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .certificate::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 24px;
      left: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      bottom: 24px;
      border: 0.5px solid rgba(212, 197, 169, 0.5);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* Header */
    .cert-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .university-name {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--red);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .university-en {
      font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--red), transparent);
      margin: 20px 0;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .cert-title {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--ink);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .cert-number {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* Body */
    .cert-body {
      line-height: 2.2;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-align: justify;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .cert-body p {
      text-indent: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .highlight-name {
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 17px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .highlight-field {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .cert-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-top: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .footer-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .footer-block {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .footer-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }

    .footer-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .seal-area {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .seal {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid var(--red);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--red);
      font-weight: 900;
      position: relative;
      opacity: 0.85;
      transform: rotate(-12deg);
    }

    .seal::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 4px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--red);
    }

    .seal-top {
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .seal-star {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 2px 0;
    }

    .seal-bottom {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .seal-date {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    }

    /* Watermark */
    .watermark {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-30deg);
      font-size: 100px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.035);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      white-space: nowrap;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
    }

    /* Corner ornaments */
    .corner {
      position: absolute;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .corner-tl { top: 30px; left: 30px; border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); }
    .corner-tr { top: 30px; right: 30px; border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); border-right: 2px solid var(--gold); }
    .corner-bl { bottom: 30px; left: 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); }
    .corner-br { bottom: 30px; right: 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); border-right: 2px solid var(--gold); }

    /* Print button */
    .print-bar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 24px;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .print-btn {
      padding: 10px 28px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .print-btn:hover {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border-color: var(--ink);
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: white; padding: 0; }
      .print-bar { display: none; }
      .certificate { box-shadow: none; border-color: #999; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .certificate { padding: 40px 32px 36px; }
      .university-name { font-size: 24px; }
      .cert-title { font-size: 20px; }
      .cert-body { font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; }
      .cert-footer { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 28px; }
      .seal-area { align-self: center; }
    }
  </style>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="certificate">
      <div class="watermark" aria-hidden="true">证明</div>
      <div class="corner corner-tl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="corner corner-tr" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="corner corner-bl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="corner corner-br" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="cert-header">
        <div class="university-name">南 昌 大 学</div>
        <div class="university-en">Nanchang University</div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="cert-title">在 职 教 师 证 明</div>
        <div class="cert-number">编号：NCU-2026-CS-060201</div>
      </div>

      <div class="cert-body">
        <p>
          兹证明 <span class="highlight-name">刘锦荣（Liu Jinrong）</span> 同志，
          自入职以来，一直在我校 <span class="highlight-field">计算机科学与技术学院</span>
          任职，现任 <span class="highlight-field">计算机教师</span>，从事计算机科学相关课程的教学与科研工作。
        </p>
        <p>
          该同志在我校工作期间，恪守教师职业道德规范，认真履行岗位职责，
          教学态度端正，工作表现良好，现仍在我校正常任职。
        </p>
        <p>
          本证明仅用于证明该同志的在职情况，特此证明。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cert-footer">
        <div class="footer-left">
          <div class="footer-block">
            <span class="footer-label">开具单位</span>
            <span class="footer-value">南昌大学人事处</span>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-block">
            <span class="footer-label">开具日期</span>
            <span class="footer-value">2026 年 6 月 2 日</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="seal-area">
          <div class="seal" aria-label="南昌大学公章">
            <span class="seal-top">南昌大学</span>
            <span class="seal-star">&#9733;</span>
            <span class="seal-bottom">人事处</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="print-bar">
      <button class="print-btn" onclick="window.print()">打印证明</button>
      <button class="print-btn" onclick="history.back()">返回</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
